{"id":10635,"date":"2024-03-03T13:44:15","date_gmt":"2024-03-03T13:44:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.screeningdate.com\/?p=10635"},"modified":"2024-03-30T17:22:50","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:22:50","slug":"jacobs-university-scholarships","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/jacobs-university-scholarships\/","title":{"rendered":"Jacobs University Masters Scholarship, Germany"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Jacobs University Scholarship for international students is provided to assist Masters students in Germany. Find the scholarship link now.<\/p><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_65 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-light-blue ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Contents on This Page<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/jacobs-university-scholarships\/#Scholarship_Coverage\" title=\"Scholarship Coverage\">Scholarship Coverage<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/jacobs-university-scholarships\/#Scholarship_Summary\" title=\"Scholarship Summary\">Scholarship Summary<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/jacobs-university-scholarships\/#Eligibility_Criteria_for_Jacobs_University_Scholarships\" title=\"Eligibility Criteria for Jacobs University Scholarships\">Eligibility Criteria for Jacobs University Scholarships<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/jacobs-university-scholarships\/#How_to_Apply_for_Jacobs_University_Scholarships\" title=\"How to Apply for Jacobs University Scholarships?\">How to Apply for Jacobs University Scholarships?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-5' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-5'><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-5' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-5'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/jacobs-university-scholarships\/#Documents_Required_During_Application\" title=\"Documents Required During Application\">Documents Required During Application<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<h2 id=\"scholarship-coverage\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Scholarship_Coverage\"><\/span>Scholarship Coverage<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Jacobs University Graduate Scholarships provide the students with below benefits:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>All applicants for the MSc Data Engineering,\u00a0MSc in Data Science for Society &amp; Business and the MSc Supply Chain Management are considered for merit-based scholarships of up to \u20ac 12,000 per year.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"scholarship-summary\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Scholarship_Summary\"><\/span>Scholarship Summary<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Level of Study:\u00a0<\/strong>Masters<\/li>\n<li><strong>Institution(s):<\/strong>\u00a0Jacobs University Bremen<\/li>\n<li><strong>Study in:<\/strong>\u00a0Germany<\/li>\n<li><b>Opportunity Focus Areas:<\/b>\n<ul>\n<li>MSc in Data Engineering<\/li>\n<li>MSc in Data Science for Society &amp; Business<\/li>\n<li>MSc in Supply Chain Management<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><b>Program Period:\u00a0<\/b>2 years<\/li>\n<li><b><strong>Deadline:<\/strong><\/b>\u00a0June 01, 2024<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Read Also&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-keep-to-your-screening-interview-date\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">How to Keep to your Screening &amp; Interview Date<\/a><\/p>\n<h3 id=\"eligibility-criteria-for-jacobs-university-scholarships\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Eligibility_Criteria_for_Jacobs_University_Scholarships\"><\/span>Eligibility Criteria for Jacobs University Scholarships<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>To qualify for Jacobs University Graduate Scholarships, the candidate must fulfil all of the following requirements below:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Required Language:\u00a0<\/strong>English.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Eligible Countries:\u00a0<\/strong>All world countries<\/li>\n<li>Citizens of all nationalities are eligible.<\/li>\n<li>Bachelor\u2019s degree certificate or equivalent (may be handed in later)<\/li>\n<li><strong>CV<\/strong>\u00a0describes your academic and professional information, extracurricular and voluntary activities<\/li>\n<li>Bachelor&#8217;s transcript in English or German.<\/li>\n<li>English language proficiency test with a minimum score of 90 (TOEFL), 6.5 (IELTS) or 110 (Duolingo).<\/li>\n<li>Two\u00a0<strong>recommendation letters<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"content\" class=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n<article id=\"post-85063\" class=\"post-85063 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-degree-scholarships category-post-doc tag-i-am-not-sure-whether-this-ooportunity-is-fully-funded-or-not tag-in-the-apply-now-link-i-couldnt-find-the-application-link-because-its-not-available-yet-so-i-put-the-link-which-was-in-the-official-website-of-the-online-application-but-its-not-uploaded-yet tag-salma-aladdin regions-australia regions-australia-oceania funding-type-fullyfunded nationality-algeria-en nationality-bahrain-en nationality-comoros-en nationality-cyprus-en nationality-djibouti-en nationality-egypt-en nationality-iran-en nationality-iraq-en nationality-jordan-en nationality-kuwait-en nationality-lebanon-en nationality-libya-en nationality-mauritania-en nationality-morocco-en nationality-oman-en nationality-palestine-en nationality-qatar-en nationality-saudi-arabia-en nationality-somalia-en nationality-sudan-en nationality-syria-en nationality-tunisia-en nationality-turkey-en nationality-uae-en nationality-yemen-en fields-type-accounting-en fields-type-aerospace-engineering fields-type-agriculture-and-veterinary-medicine fields-type-agriculture fields-type-anthropology fields-type-applied-and-pure-sciences-en fields-type-archaeology fields-type-architecture fields-type-architecture-construction-en fields-type-art fields-type-astronomy fields-type-biology fields-type-biomedical-engineering fields-type-biomedical-sciences fields-type-business-and-management fields-type-business-studies fields-type-chemical-and-materials-engineering fields-type-chemistry fields-type-civil-engineering fields-type-computer-science-and-it fields-type-computing fields-type-crafts-en fields-type-creative-arts-and-desgin fields-type-criminal-law fields-type-cultural-and-critical-studies f